      <abstract>
        <p>A new Schiff base ester, 4-{[(4-methoxyphenyl)imino]methyl}-3-hydroxyphenyl 4-(hexadecanoyloxy)benzoate was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR and MS spectroscopic data are presented.</p>
      </abstract>
